{"tid":471154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逼睇京官】左報涉屈學生「未夠喉 想聽多次」","createTime":"2017-11-17T03:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T04:41:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"daf46c9b5c6e5cb0dbbb425bdd91f8fbdbe2b25e","tid":471154,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171117/large/1510889756_e9ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171117%2Flarge%2F1510889756_e9ec.png&h=8524e168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至少50間中學應教育局「邀請」，早上安排學生收看基本法委員會主任李飛在《基本法》研討會的演講直播，惟不少學生被乏味演辭、沉悶的聲線「催眠」，打瞌睡的大有人在。不過左報《文匯報》卻活在平行時空，縱然內文指有中六生稱，若有類似課題，「不介意聽多一次」，不過標題卻寫成「睇直播未夠喉 中六生想聽多次」，不但相當「擦鞋」，亦似乎扭曲學生的原意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171117/57469225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57469225&d=j3GOyvcuxBwnVifK%2BrcsgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=661b2b32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171117%2F57469225&h=1d8dd075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171117/57469225</a>"},{"pid":"f01520427659d01735b5e29943a8aa84905a9093","tid":471154,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"北韓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902fc99d564e17e5b8851b846bba05d972414864","tid":471154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"份報紙垃圾到藍絲都唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}